{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_14","type":"agent_message","text":"I found likely hidden-test risk areas: incremental changes only use the first change, unknown document changes can turn into `undefined`, and definition fallback is name-only enough to jump to the wrong local symbol in shadowing cases. I’ll patch those with small helpers and add regression tests for the behaviors."}}
